{"word":"G2352 - θραύω - thraúō - throw'-o - Bruise","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θραύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thraúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">throw'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bruise</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நொறுக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to break, to break in pieces, to shatter, to smite through"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to <i>crush</i>: - bruise. Compare <a href=\"#/G4486 - ῥήγνυμι - rhḗgnymi - hrayg'-noo-mee/4486\">G4486</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}